Steps:

1) Set JAVA_HOME environment variable to existing JRE/JDK installation pointing to the java directory
2) Run the file /bin/run.sh
3) After software has been successfully started, goto http://localhost:8080/
4) Click bounce now link and enter your yad2 credentials
5) Click bounce, that's it
6) Enjoy!



Change default execution port:

Set PORT environment variable with the desired port